text: The Promised Land () is a 1973 Chilean Cuban drama movie directed by Miguel Littín and starring Nelson Villagra, Marcelo Gaete, Rafael Benavente, Shenda Román, Pedro Manuel Álvarez. ==Other websites== * Category:1973 drama movies Category:Chilean movies Category:Cuban movies Category:Movies directed by Miguel Littín
